---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About — Ian Hogers" side="neutral">
  <section class="py-6">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
      <img src="/assets/pixel-art/game-assets/overlord_statue_active.png" alt="" class="pixel-sprite w-12 h-12 animate-float" />
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-0">About</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="pixel-box p-6 mb-8">
      <div class="prose">
        <p>I'm <strong>Ian</strong> — also known as <strong class="text-violet-400">SanCoca</strong> online. Dutch-Australian software engineer and game developer based in the real world, building things that work.</p>
        <p>I've been writing code since I was a kid and never really stopped. I build websites, games, tools, and whatever else needs building. If there's a problem, I solve it. If there's a thing that should exist, I make it.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
      <div class="pixel-box pixel-box-lavender p-5">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
          <img src="/assets/pixel-art/game-assets/wow_blue.png" alt="" class="pixel-sprite w-5 h-5" />
          <h2 class="text-xl text-purple-300 mb-0">Dev Side</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Software engineering, AI agents, game development, technical deep-dives. The stuff that pays the bills and keeps the brain sharp.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pixel-box pixel-box-amber p-5">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
          <img src="/assets/pixel-art/decorative/sample-bunny.png" alt="" class="pixel-sprite w-5 h-5" />
          <h2 class="text-xl text-amber-400 mb-0">Life Side</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Cooking, baking, bunny rescue, voice acting, crafts, and whatever else I'm into. The stuff that keeps me human.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="prose mb-8">
      <h2>How I work</h2>
      <p>Direct. No-nonsense. I'd rather ship something good today than talk about shipping something perfect next quarter. If you want meetings about meetings, I'm the wrong person. If you want stuff done — let's go.</p>

      <h2>Get in touch</h2>
      <p>Find me online as <strong class="text-violet-400">SanCoca</strong> or reach out at <a href="mailto:ian@ianhogers.com">ian@ianhogers.com</a>.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-gray-600 font-mono">
      <img src="/assets/pixel-art/decorative/star_grow.png" alt="" class="pixel-sprite w-4 h-4 animate-sparkle opacity-40" />
      <span>Same person, different modes. Pick your side, or read both.</span>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
